claim.claim-text:
Vehicle comprising:
an engine (14) having an intake port (17a);
a fixed funnel (26) for introducing air to the intake port (17a) of the engine (14);
a movable funnel (27,77) movably disposed on an air supply side of the fixed funnel (26) for introducing the air to the intake port (17a) of the engine (14) in conjunction with the fixed funnel (26);
a seal member (35,85) disposed between the fixed funnel (26) and the movable funnel (27,77); and
an engagement part for engagement of the seal member (35,85) with either one of the fixed funnel (26) and the movable funnel (27,77) to prevent the seal member (35,85) from falling off.
